Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sama sekali di wajah Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beda banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerja bagus, Manajer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bikin nostalgia saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, dia masih hidup, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pesan dari mantan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang sudah lama pacaran dengannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang tiba-tiba hilang tanpa penjelasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudnya "LOL"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia enggak bisa bilang "maaf"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cowok dan harga diri mereka…\NMenyebalkan banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lupakan saja, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tahu, kan,
