Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sama sekali enggak paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau maafkan dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benar-benar enggak mengerti,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi mending kita melakukan\Nhal yang seru saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kejujuranmu itu penyelamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kehidupan anak sekolah\Nbukan cuma soal cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita main boling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tiba-tiba ngomong begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya aku lagi ingin main boling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu cuma perasaanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma ingin lempar benda berat\Nsekuat tenaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tujuan macam apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu di akhir pekan…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azuma bilang keretanya ditunda,\Njadi dia agak telat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira Taira-Azuma datang bareng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan menggabungkan nama kami begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah stasiun terdekat kalian sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau kenalan kami lihat\Nkami ketemuan di stasiun yang sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa dengan Azu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kombinasi macam apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf bikin kalian menunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membayangkannya saja
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sudah bikin aku keringat dingin…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pertama kalinya kau main boling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulu aku pernah main boling\Nsaat masih di perkumpulan bocah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ada yang kau enggak mengerti,\Nnanti kuajari, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, sepatu boling dibuat jelek\Nbiar enggak dicuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya dia perlu tahu itu?
