Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku malah dapat 50…
