Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya, godai dia itu seru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian lihat itu, kan?
