Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak-anak "Aku Cinta Kampung Halamanku".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka masih sering kumpul, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku enggak lihat mereka,
