Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagian, kurasa mereka sudah lupa sama aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seingatku, Azuma lumayan dekat sama mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak mau mereka mengajak ngobrol\Nsaat aku lagi bareng kalian.
