Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pacar mereka sekarang, si 3 dan 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ngomong apa, sih?
