Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak masalah,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kayaknya mereka\Nyang menutup-nutupi sesuatu, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba aku dapat chat dari si 1
