Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus dia jadian sama si 3\Nenggak lama setelahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau panggil mereka pakai angka…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus si 2, yang tadinya dekat denganku,\Ntiba-tiba putus kontak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelahnya aku baru tahu dia pacaran sama 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, dia malah dekati aku dan 4\Nsecara bersamaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perasaannya susah dijelaskan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kacau banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sampai merinding mendengarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa-bisanya mereka pacaran dan putus\Nkayak lagi tukar-menukar kartu,
