Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku malah dapat pesan dari 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Kau main boling hari ini? LOL."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pintar banget pura-pura bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sikapnya kelihatan jelas banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya lumayan lucu, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau seharusnya marah, dong!
