Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan cowok yang masih coba mendekatimu\Nsetelah sekian lama,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka enggak berani menghadapimu\Natau kasih penjelasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi mereka juga enggak mau\Nkelihatan kayak orang jahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu benar-benar kurang ajar, lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau berhak marah saat orang-orang\Nmemperlakukanmu dengan buruk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuma kau yang menderita di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sama sekali enggak adil buatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kau tahu, kan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau aku sudah suka sama seseorang,\Nsusah banget buat benci mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pun yang terjadi,\Naku ujung-ujungnya cuma bisa maafkan mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya orang-orang\Nmemperlakukan aku seperti itu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kita enggak benci seseorang,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa kita harus maafkan dan\Nterima semua kekurangan mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh banget, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hal itu yang selama ini menggangguku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak pernah memikirkan itu\Nterlalu serius
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sampai bisa mengungkapkannya kayak Taira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lupakan saja, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau malah maafkan dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum aku bilang\Naku enggak diperlakukan dengan baik
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau lagi apes urusan cowok,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin aku yang terlalu abai\Nsama diriku sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Taira, makasih sudah…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benar-benar minta maaf soal kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sok tahu dan ngomong macam-macam,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi setelah kupikir-pikir,\Napa hakku ngomong begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir, "Kalau itu aku, aku bakal marah,"\Ndan langsung asal ngomong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku bisa ngomong begitu\Ncuma karena aku orang luar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu memang sifat burukku.\NAku enggak tahan kalau lihat ketidakadilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bawaannya ingin kasih pendapat terus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pendapatmu…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau sekadar kasih pendapat,\Nenggak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi mencoba mengatur-atur perasaanmu\Nitu salah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baru sadar setelahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke, aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya sudahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Maafkan apanya?\N- Kumaafkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Miyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhir pekan ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kayaknya kakak dan ayahmu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lagi enggak ada di rumah, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf ya, tiba-tiba minta kau datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kejauhan\Nkalau kau enggak naik sepeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya hari ini kayaknya bakal hujan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini intuisinya nenekku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena ada alasan yang masuk akal
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}buat pesan makanan, aku jadi semangat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, ayo masuk…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf mengganggu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kelihatan sopan banget, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Tante!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lewat sini, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tinggal di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Di kota sebelah…\N- Ya ampun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jalan jauh-jauh ke sini pasti capek banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu, jangan disela terus, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ada makanan yang enggak kau suka,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}enggak usah dipaksakan makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagian, bukan aku yang masak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Malah ngomong yang enggak perlu.\N- Makasih, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau suka makan apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harusnya aku tanya dari awal, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu tanya banyak hal, tapi malah\Nmenyediakan yang enggak bisa dia makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun, gawat banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau kita putar musik?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau dengar Official Bearded Baron, enggak?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak muda suka itu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu, tenang dikit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanti Ibu bawakan camilan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, ya, ibuku terlalu gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlalu gugup?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelihatan banget gugupnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana ngomongnya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa,\Nkelihatan banget kalau dia ibumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu pujian atau bukan, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pastinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar-benar hujan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa bakal reda saat kau pulang nanti?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku suka banget hujan
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau lagi di rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya redup meskipun lagi siang,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}terus di luar lagi hujan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hujan saat kencan di rumah\Nitu memang yang terbaik!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kencan belajar saat musim panas\Njuga asyik.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Intinya, dua-duanya sama-sama seru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku terlalu banyak ngomong sendiri, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak berhak ngomel ke ibuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, Tani pendiam banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibuku bilang bakal bawakan camilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai saat itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus habis itu bagaimana, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Miyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktunya makan camilan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun, hujannya lebih deras\Ndari dugaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertandingan bisbol amatirnya dibatalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, ada tamu di kamar Miyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu ini agak telat bilangnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi Tani lagi ada di kamarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hujannya deras banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga hujannya reda saat kau pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi aku juga ngomong begitu, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus bagaimana?\NMesti bilang apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, mungkin lebih baik aku diam saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau duduk lebih dekat denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin dipeluk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebaiknya jangan sampai kena lipstik.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jantungmu berdebar kencang banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhenti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejujurnya, kau itu susah banget dimengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kau mendadak diam,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}suasananya jadi canggung.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memang payah kalau soal begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak apa-apa, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yusuke Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yusuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yusuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma coba panggil nama yang berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yu, Yu, Suke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Miyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan formal-formal amat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dik Miyu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh juga, tuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Miyu…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku belum terbiasa dengan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemeja Hawaii-nya bikin nostalgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku bertemu temannya Miyu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}enggak boleh terlihat memalukan, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani sudah mau pulang.\NAku antar dia ke depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, begini…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia ini pacarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pacar…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pacar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Siapa namamu?\N- Namaku Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, maksudnya nama depanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yusuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yusuke, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berapa umurmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kau sekolah di mana?\N- Sayang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ngobrolnya nanti saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku masih ingin tahu lebih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah alasannya
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku enggak mau kau bertemu sama dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf ya, orang tuaku memang berisik banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menertawakan semuanya terus dari tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:20:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah bagaimana…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}orang tuamu, teman-temanmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan semua hal di masa lalumu itu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bikin aku merasa kalau semua itulah\Nyang membentuk dirimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malu banget, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Seluk-beluk Suzuki"?\NMemangnya potongan tubuh Suzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Musim gugur sudah tiba, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya udaranya lembap sehabis hujan\Ndi pertengahan musim panas,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi hujan saat pergantian musim itu\Nrasanya beda banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Betul.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hawanya persis seperti ini\Nsaat festival budaya SMP kita selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak saat itu,\Ntiap kali merasakan angin sejuk ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku jadi merasa festival tahun ini\Njuga sudah kelar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayaknya aku bakal ngomong hal\Nyang sama juga tahun depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mulai sekarang, tiap kali merasakan\Nudara yang sama seperti ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan teringat hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengar…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengar kau ngomong begitu…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga jadi mulai merasakan\Nhal yang sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.16,0:22:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang enggak boleh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Miyu sekarang sudah punya pacar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan minum-minum sebelum makan malam, ya.
